#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items description
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "The app is designed with privacy in mind - does not identify people, does not track you, and does not collect any information."
msgstr "Appen er designet med fokus på privatlivets fred – den identificerer ikke personer, sporer dig ikke og indsamler ikke oplysninger."

