#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items description
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Efficiently uses the battery, doesn’t drain your battery like other navigation apps."
msgstr "Bruger batteriet effektivt og dræner ikke dit batteri ligesom andre navigationsapps."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items highlight text
