#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra funding items text
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Currently there is no full time team who is working to develop new features and improve the service. To consistently move the product forward, a core team is needed."
msgstr "Der er endnu ikke nogen, der arbejder med nye funktioner eller forbedringer af Comaps på fuld tid. For at sikre stabil drift og udvikling af appen, er det nødvendigt med et fast personale."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra funding items title
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Developers"
msgstr "Udviklere"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra funding items text
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "We pay for fast servers, so anyone in the world can download free map data updates without delays. The maps data transfers are hundreds of terabytes monthly, and the amount is growing."
msgstr "Vi betaler for hurtige server så alle verden over kan hente gratis kortopdateringer uden forsinkelse. Der overføres hundredevis af terabyte om måneden og datamængden stiger kun."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra funding items title
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Infrastructure"
msgstr "Infrastruktur"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra funding items text
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "User support, fixing bugs, and improving the stability of the app are our top priority. The list of requests and bug reports grows every day, and there are many support requests to respond to on the App Store, Google Play, and support emails."
msgstr "Brugersupport, fejlretning og forbedring af ydeevne er vores topprioriteter. Listen med ønsker til nye funktioner og meddelses om fejl vokser hver eneste dag, og der er mange support-anmodninger at svare på i App Store, Google Play og pr. e-mail."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/donate/index.md content/support/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support"
msgstr "Support"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra funding title
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "How will funding be used?"
msgstr "Hvordan vil midlerne blive anvendt?"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra info text
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "We rely on your donations to keep CoMaps open and free"
msgstr "Vi er afhængige af dine donationer for at holde CoMaps åben og gratis"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra info text
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "We are a few enthusiasts contributing in our free time. We love what we do, and we love our users"
msgstr "Vi er en gruppe entusiaster, der bidrager i vores fritid. Vi elsker det, vi laver, og vi elsker vores brugere"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra info text
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "With your support, we are working toward privacy-focused map navigation that is the preferred choice on the market"
msgstr "Med din støtte arbejder vi på at udvikle en privatlivsfokuseret kortnavigation, der bliver det foretrukne valg på markedet"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: description
#: content/support/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Need assistance? Search for answers to common questions. Get the support you need and connect with others in the community for help."
msgstr "Brug for hjælp? Søg efter svar på typiske spørgsmål. Få den support, du har brug for, og kontakt andre i fællesskabet for at få hjælp."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: description
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Free and open navigation with privacy -<br/>Built by the community"
msgstr "Fri og åben navigation med privatlivsbeskyttelse -<br/>Bygget af fællesskabet"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra about text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "CoMaps is a community-focused privacy navigation app for travelers - drivers, hikers, and cyclists. It uses the crowd-sourced OpenStreetMap data with contributors from all over the globe. It offers navigation with privacy - no identifying people and no data collection. CoMaps features can operate without an active internet connection for offline navigation at urban or distant locations, where cellular service is not available. CoMaps is an open-source project, and prioritizes community development."
msgstr "CoMaps er en fællesskabsorienteret navigationsapp med fokus på beskyttelse af privatlivets fred for rejsende – bilister, vandrere og cyklister. Den bruger crowd-sourcede OpenStreetMap-data med bidrag fra hele verden. Den tilbyder navigation med beskyttelse af privatlivets fred – ingen identifikation af personer og ingen dataindsamling. CoMaps-funktionerne fungerer uden en aktiv internetforbindelse, så der kan navigeres offline i byområder eller afsides egne, hvor der ikke er mobildækning. CoMaps er et open source-projekt, der prioriterer udvikling af fællesskabet."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra about title
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Free and open navigation with privacy, built by the community"
msgstr "Fri og åben navigation med privatlivsbeskyttelse, udviklet af fællesskabet"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "MapsWithMe navigation app created (later renamed to Maps.me)."
msgstr "Navigationsappen MapsWithMe oprettes (senere omdøbt til Maps.me)."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Maps.me opened the source code under Apache 2.0 license."
msgstr "Maps.me gjorde kildekoden tilgængelig under Apache 2.0-licensen."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Organic Maps project & company were founded, based on the Maps.Me source code."
msgstr "Organic Maps-projektet og -virksomheden blev grundlagt på basis af Maps.Me-kildekoden."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Governance issues and community concerns not addressed by company shareholders stalled the development of Organic Maps for months."
msgstr "Governance-spørgsmål og bekymringer fra fællesskabet, som ikke blev adresseret af virksomhedens aktionærer, forsinkede udviklingen af Organic Maps i flere måneder."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **CoMaps** community & non-profit project was founded by former Organic Maps contributors, based on the Organic Maps source code."
msgstr "**CoMaps**-fællesskabet og non-profit-projektet blev grundlagt af tidligere bidragydere til Organic Maps på basis af Organic Maps' kildekode."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history title
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "History"
msgstr "Historie"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra vm items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Unlock the freedom to easily navigate offline, with privacy-focused maps for drivers, hikers, and cyclists, powered by the community."
msgstr "Få friheden til nemt at navigere offline med privatlivsfokuserede kort til bilister, vandrere og cyklister, drevet af fællesskabet."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra vm items title
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mission"
msgstr "Mission"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra vm items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create a world where navigating with maps is free, and privacy by default is the top choice on the planet."
msgstr "Skab en verden, hvor navigation med kort er gratis, og hvor privatlivets fred som standard er det foretrukne valg på kloden."

